LETRA:
**CUARENTA**

Hoy tengo la suerte de ser ésta que al fin soy
Ninguna de veinte te da lo que yo te doy
Tu me llamas y cuando quieras salimos
Y así te muestro todo lo que yo he aprendido.

Tu me llamas, tengo un par de truquitos
Pero te advierto pueden ser adictivos
Y cuando lo sientas te vas a dar cuenta
Lo que te doy no te lo da ninguna nena
Y cuando lo sientas sacarás la cuenta
Con dos de veinte no haces una de cuarenta.

Ah ah ah , lo que te doy no te lo da ninguna nena
Con dos de veinte no haces una de Cuarenta…

Cuarenta primaveras buenísima y con la cartera llena
No me hace falta nada, hoy voy a bailar la noche entera
No estoy buscando promesas, tampoco quien me mantenga,
Lo que yo quiero es brindar por todo y que siga la fiesta.

Tu me llamas y cuando quieras salimos
Y tu me enseñas todo lo que has aprendido
Tu me llamas, tienes par de truquitos
Que me dijeron pueden ser adictivos.

Y cuando lo sientas te vas a dar cuenta
Lo que te doy no lo vas a encontrar en ella.

La la la solo debate llevar
Una noche pa gozar
Ah ah
Que la que sabe hace la diferencia.

title: Mandirwa | Bhimpalasi | Lokdhuncafe | Supriya Joshi | Music Video | Mumbai
description:
Hi Folk, 
As you know that I have come from a classical music background where I learned many ragas and so many things from my Gurus.
This is my favorite Bandish of Raag Bhimpalasi.

In this video, we tried to show the feeling of a lower-middle-class working woman and things that are going through her mind regarding her travel, office work,  Boss and so many things.
 her home is like a temple where she feels peace and happiness and at the end of the day she found her peace when she reaches home. 
 
This Bandish I learned almost 18  years back and it was in my mind and in my daily practice too. so now Mandirwa is for you.
Pls, Do share, like, Comment and subscribe to the channel and show your love ❤️

title: Andrea Sannino - 1985
description:
1985 
(A.Sannino – A.Spenillo – M.Spenillo)

Ehi, abbassa un po’ il finestrino
Guarda quanta gente ca parla e cammina
Oggi nun se guardene cchiu, nun parlano cchiù, 
Pe’ furtuna ce stai tu
Ca me fai scurdà tutt’e pensieri
Sentimento d’ajere
Fore a nu’ chalet, pure sulo io e te, ‘na cassetta che gira

Senza se fermà, nun te vuò arritirà
‘o viento ‘nfaccia e ‘a voglia d’alluccà

E nun c’abbasta ‘na vita
Cu’ tte so’ sicuro ca ce ne vò n’ata
Nun è mai fernute, nun è mai passato
Pecchè ‘o tiempo mi si sempe tu, stasera
Dimme ca me vuò cchiù bene
Dimme ca è cchiù assaje d’ajere

Eh si, hai ragione tu
Ce sta ‘o sciopero ‘a cumana nun passa cchiù
Pure si ‘a partita sta pe’ ferni, ce fanno trasi, avviammece a’ppere
Si cchiù bella e ‘na bella canzone
Tu si cchiù ‘e Maradona
Senza nù pecchè, ce truvamme io e te dinte ‘a machina a’nnure

Senza ce fermà, nun te vuò arritirà
‘o viento ‘nfaccia e ‘a voglia d’alluccà

E nun c’abbasta ‘na vita
Cu’ tte so’ sicuro ca ce ne vò n’ata
Nun è mai fernute, nun è mai passato
Pecchè ‘o tiempo mi si sempe tu, stasera
Dimme ca me vuò cchiù bene

A nuie c’abbasta nu poco
‘a luce stutata, nu vaso arrubbato
‘na stanza cu ‘o cielo e ‘a radio appicciata
tiempo ca un conta niente cchiuù, stasera
dimme ca me vuò cchiù bene,
dimme ca è cchiu assaje da  ajere

…vedi quell’estate è finita
e ‘a vita mia è accumminciata.

Regia

Hayden Williams-Moran is a 14 year-old  Singer-Songwriter and Actor from Sacramento, California. In 2021 Hayden released his first EP, featuring his first original song "Avila Beach", and his second EP Album in 2022.  Hayden focused on finding his "Happy Ending" with his last album and original songs for 2022.  Now he is releasing his first Original for 2023 "UNDERSTANDING ONE ANOTHER". title: «Хатнi» пiць — са смакам жыць!
description:
Варта пачуць першы радок, як успамінаеш той самы верш, які вучыў калісьці,
той самы дом, у якім збіралася сям'я,
той самы смак страў, прыгатаваных з любоўю самымі блізкімі,
тую асалоду, якую так лёгка адчуць.
Варта зрабіць глыток таго самага квасу, які памятаеш ты і які памятае цябе,
тое самае важнае, што ведаеш на памяць і адчуваеш усім сэрцам.
 
Квас «Хатнi» — высакаякасны беларускi хлебны квас 100% натуральнага браджэння, які прыйдзецца даспадобы ўсім членам сям'і.

«Хатнi» пiць — са смакам жыць!

title: Clinical Pharmacology Modeling and Simulation (CPMS)
description:
Allucent's dedicated team of Clinical Pharmacology Modeling and Simulation experts collaborates closely with our partners to optimize their clinical and nonclinical studies, encompassing candidate selection, first-in-human trials, proof of concept, and beyond.

In the field of drug development, Clinical Pharmacology Modeling and Simulation plays a vital role in evaluating how the body interacts with the drug and how the drug impacts the body. It involves understanding patient variability and establishing connections between this variability and factors such as benefit, risk, and dosing. Each in vitro, non-clinical, and clinical study is meticulously designed to address key questions essential for development milestones, all with the ultimate aim of comprehending the drug's value for patients.

By integrating information obtained from these studies at various phases of development, along with relevant published data, we employ model-informed approaches. These approaches allow us to provide quantitative insights into dosing options, design features that enhance study efficiency, patient selection criteria, and pharmacokinetic/pharmacodynamic (PK/PD) assessments. These assessments are crucial for answering pivotal questions related to different patient and clinical scenarios throughout the drug development journey, starting from candidate selection and continuing through regulatory approval and beyond.

To learn more about Allucent's Clinical Pharmacology Modeling and Simulation services, please visit:
https://www.allucent.com/clinical-research-services/clinical-pharmacology-modeling-simulation

Additionally, we invite you to explore our Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics (PK/PD) capabilities, which play an integral role in our approach:
https://www.allucent.com/clinical-research-services/clinical-pharmacology-modeling-simulation/pharmacokinetics-and-pharmacodynamics-pkpd 

For further information about Allucent and to connect with us, please visit:

title: Deploy your SSH Key for Intel® VTune™ Profiler | Intel Software
description:
Intel VTune Profiler can collect workload performance data locally or on a remote target. In this video we show how to configure remote data collection on a remote Linux* target. This includes setup and creation of a trusted SSH based communication channel.

The first time you start the Intel VTune Profiler graphical user interface, create a project and then click the configure analysis button in the menu or in the welcome tab.

To configure a remote Linux* target system, mouse click in the Where Pane and select Remote Linux.

Specify the user name and network name or IP address of the target system.

VTune Profiler communicates with the target system with passwordless SSH using a private / public key pair.
If this is not already set up, VTune Profiler creates the key pair in the user's home .ssh directory and deploys the public key to the target system's authorized keys file in the home .ssh directory.

Click the Deploy button to install the data collection drivers on the target system.

On the target system, VTune Profiler creates or appends the authorized keys file in the user's home .ssh 
directory and installs the data collection drivers in the temp vtune profiler target directory.

The data collection driver source code is in the sepdk src subdirectory, with some useful scripts to rebuild and reload the drivers, and query the current driver status.

Intel® VTune™ Profiler: https://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/developer/tools/oneapi/vtune-profiler.html

title: Santa Musa - Loco (Video Oficial)
description:
Santa Musa - Loco (Video Oficial)

“Loco” es un tema hecho bajo un estilo de fusión entre las formas orgánicas del Gypsy Jazz, Pop e indudablemente el género Urbano. De una forma alegre y romántica se ve plasmada la locura que genera el amor en una persona cuando el sentimiento es intenso. Arreglos de voces, guitarras, percusiones y sintetizadores hacen del tema una liga de lo viejo y lo nuevo apto para todo tipo de público y en cualquier edad.

title: Semana presencial de los Programas en Alta Dirección (Video Recap)
description:
Nuestros Programas en Alta Dirección ofrecen un camino de aprendizaje inmersivo para managers y líderes de alto potencial con experiencia contrastada que aspiren a convertirse en directivos C-Level exitosos. Esta formación semipresencial permite a los participantes tener las ventajas de aprender a través de la educación online y asistir a dos semanas presenciales en el campus de MIT. En estas semanas presenciales, cuentan con workshops, escuchan a expertos invitados especiales y acceden a una network exclusiva con Faculty del MIT y ejecutivos de todo el mundo. 

👉 Obtén más información sobre nuestros Programas en Alta Dirección: https://professional.mit.edu/

title: Historia FEMSA
Let's do better to #beatplasticpollution this World Environment Day 2023
description:
World Environment Day 2023 is a reminder that people’s actions on plastic pollution matters. The steps governments and businesses are taking to tackle plastic pollution are the consequence of this action.

It is time to accelerate this action and transition to a circular economy. It is time to #beatplasticpollution 

Learn more: https://www.worldenvironmentday.global/

Please note: you can change the audio track of this video into all official UN languages.

SCRIPT:

Plastic has been a solution. It has given humanity: convenience, affordability, utility.

However, the durability of plastic is both its benefit and its curse. Plastic pollution endures. It’s suffocating our planet.

We have seen solutions that work: rejecting single-use plastics, enforcing bans on single-use plastics, creating circular and sustainable alternatives, managing plastic waste more efficiently.

Together, let’s create systems to better reuse, reduce and recycle.
Together, Let’s push for an ambitious global agreement to end plastic pollution.
Together, Let’s demand governments and businesses
act, commit and set new standards.

Use your voice and your choice
to #beatplasticpollution 
Let’s do better.

Hi Ren is out now on all streaming platforms
https://renmakesmusic.lnk.to/hiren

Creating this song wasn't easy, but I'm so proud of how it turned out. 

Want to say a big thank you for everyones support over the years. During the years trapped inside with chronic health problems  the main thing that kept me going was a belief that one day I would come out the other side, and be able to achieve success through music. I don’t have a label, and sometimes pushing these things as hard as I want becomes a massive challenge, and I find myself frustrated that there aren’t enough hours in the day to push it as far as I want to. I would love to ask a favour to anyone who has ever enjoyed my music over the years, and it will only take a few minutes of your day.It would  mean the world to me if you shared ‘Hi Ren’ as much as you can, over social media platforms, with friends, over email. Together, and with your help I can hopefully reach people all over the world, and get one step closer to the dream I always had! Thank you so much for the support so far!

title: Luigi Gagliotti - Sguardi (Official Video) ft Milena
description:
Gli occhi sono da sempre lo specchio dell'anima.....dagli sguardi possiamo capire tanto senza bisogno di parlare. Resta qualcosa di magico difficile da spiegare, non ho mai visto uno sguardo mentire, non ne è capace. Quello che veramente una persona ha dentro difficilmente lo capiremo dai social quindi alziamo le teste dai telefoni e torniamo a guardarci negli occhi perché che siano tristi, gioiosi, innamorati, indifferenti o bisognosi d'amore........gli sguardi sono prima di tutto veri.
La mia nuova creatura prende appunto il nome Sguardi e racconta la paura di amare. Ma dopo che il passato ti ha segnato fortemente, attraverso gli occhi di chi ti ama, ritrovi la speranza. Ho avuto l'onore di una collaborazione d'eccellenza, la voce meravigliosa di Milena che ha impreziosito il tutto. Buon ascolto.

השיר נכתב מתוך תהליך של ריפוי. מתוך נפש עייפה.. צמאה למים.. כמהה לתקווה. 
התבוננות פנימית... 
ברגע אחד הבנתי שיש לי יותר מהכל! ושום דבר לא ברור מאליו. לפעמים כל מה שאדם צריך הוא כיוון קל, מינון... אין שמחה כהתרת הספקות! להעמיק לתוכנו ולהבין עד כמה אנחנו טובים. הייתי רוצה לצעוק ולשחרר את כל האהבה הזאת החוצה.

יותר מהכל

כל מילותיי ימיי חולפים, וממרום

על מעשה ידיו

ותקבל
את קול צחוקם של ילדים, את התקווה
אנא אל תתעלם
אני רוצה שתיתן בי עוד כח, להאמין
יותר מהכל

ומה רבו המעשים והאותות
כבר לא נשאר לנו מקום הזמן בורח
האדמה צועקת אין עוד מלבדו
אני אדם פשוט שרק רוצה לשמוח

description:
今回のお客様は、元宝塚歌劇団のタレント・遼河はるひ！
男役スターとして活躍した遼河が、御曹司・八木勇征に宝塚流“カッコよく魅せるテクニック”を伝授！八木の新たな魅力が開花する！？
さらに、遼河の特技“180 度開脚”に八木＆親戚のおじさん（小沢一敬）が挑戦！
遼河式ストレッチで２人の体に変化が！？
最後に「璃月グルメ集」を見て、オリジナル杏仁豆腐作りに挑戦！一番美味しそうなのは！？

秘書　　　　　　　　　いわたまあり

遼河はるひ
 
【ナレーション】
前野智昭

人里離れた場所に建つ、古風な館。
そこに、とてつもない権力を持つ御曹司・八木勇征（FANTASTICS）が住んでいた。

さらに、大人気オープンワールドRPG『原神』でも盛り上がる！

title: Traigo Polvo del Camino // Anabella MONDI
description:
TRAIGO POLVO DEL CAMINO
el tercer cover del nuevo álbum de Anabella Mondi 
se estrena el 18 de Mayo a nivel mundial


En memoria, Augusto Bracca (1918-2012)
Honrando a nuestros maestros llaneros y a nuestro LLANO VENEZOLANO llevando este tema clásico de nuestra cultura  a nuevos géneros, latitudes y generaciones…

Anabella Mondi ha decidido sacar su tercer álbum de 14 canciones con una agenda de distribución que nos mantiene atentos y emocionados, lanzando un tema cada mes, comenzando desde los inicios de 2023 con tres clásicos llaneros como son Vestida de Garza Blanca, Fiesta en Elorza y siendo ahora el turno de Traigo Polvo del Camino, lo cual nos indica claramente que el álbum viene impregnado de sus raíces maternas llaneras que tanto la han marcado desde su infancia.

En esta ocasión TRAIGO POLVO DEL CAMINO se lanza el 18 de mayo en todas las plataformas musicales a partir de las 6 pm y con un video en YouTube  https://youtu.be/ci_U3H-mL0M  el cual muestra las maravillas del Llano adentro, su flora, su fauna, su imaginario poético y colectivo que demuestra por qué el Llano y en particular Apure es la región por excelencia de nuestra cultura, dicho en palabras de esta obra maestra de Augusto Bracca y filmado en la majestuosidad del Hato El Cedral, acervo cultural, histórico y ecológico de nuestro país.

Un equipo de la más alta producción artística, musical y visual encabezado por Hit Central Records colaboraron con Anabella bajo su dirección y producción para llevar este tema a la vanguardia sonora que ella quería plasmar, uniendo venezolanidad y tradición con transculturización y modernidad: un verdadero MESTIZAJE MODERNO; así como a través de la estética y el diseño del vestuario de la destacada diseñadora venezolana FRANCI ARIAS mostrando a la mujer llanera como mezcla de nuestras raíces indigenas con españolas. 

Su tercer álbum lleva lo mejor de la tradición llanera al mundo con su MONDI style, que es la búsqueda sonora de sonidos folclóricos con electrónica.

Para mayor información www.AnabellaMondi.com // tactuspro@gmail.com 

Gracias a LASER AIRLINES y a todos los que hicieron posible este sueño…

title: Guru Money (Guru$$) - Official Music Video
description:
(western yoga satire)

Enjoyed the video?   Please subscribe and share!  The world needs more chakra bling, yo.            

What's the vibe, my celestial tribe?

Sada Sat Bing here, dropping a cosmic comedy bomb on y'all with "Guru Money"' a parody track that digs deep into the groove of the Western Yoga scene. Feel my flow?

We got a trippy music video that takes you on a journey, featuring a pure-soul earthling bewitched by the dazzling aura of a guru. Oh, and guess who's playing that guru? You vibin' with him right now, baby!

Don't forget to like, comment, share, and subscribe for more laughs and zen vibes. Namastay cool.

--Sada Sat Bing

•☽────✧˖°˖☆˖°˖✧────☾•

Susan Rudick, Erik Passoja, Monica Kay, Katy Mikelle, Kelly Connolly, May-Har Li, Valerie Long, Leo Moctezuma, Raquel Horsford, Shannon Beach, Havord Trusty J, Jonathan Grey, Shae Lozano

www.sadasat.com

⭐️Connect with us on social media and continue the cosmic journey:
https://www.facebook.com/ErikPassojaActor/
https://www.instagram.com/erikpassoja/
https://pro.imdb.com/name/nm0664928 (reps & contact info -- professional inquiries only)

•☽────✧˖°˖☆˖°˖✧────☾•

DIRECTOR'S NOTES

Guru$$ started out as a joke. So many folks in Kundalini yoga had been given a name by Yogi Bhajan..."Gurmukh", "Sopurkh", "Sada Sat Kaur".

People asked my name. I said, "My name is Sada Sat BING" and got a laugh.

It became, "My name is Sada Sat BING, yoga's my thing."

So my new age satire life began, as I did spiritual comedy.

And then I saw what was happening in the yoga community. People think they will get the answers from one person and so they give away their power. Eventually, people, especially women, were exploited.  Not just Western Yoga.  Everywhere.

So I wrote a yoga comedy.

My little rhyme became a rap song.  Hip-hop yoga.  Comedy music about exploitation and ego, with a guru spitting old-school hip-hop. So many musical inspirations, from Slick Rick & Doug E. Fresh to Digable Planets.

Two years and three musicians later, Carl Burnett nailed it on the first pass.

We shot in 2017, again in 2018, and a little bit at the end in 2021 until we were satisfied that the story was clear. It was a lot of work but profoundly fulfilling.

Guru$$ is about a woman who tries to take a shortcut to enlightenment, gets caught up in the glitz, and ends up with nothing.

So yes, it is a comedy...

...and it is also a cautionary tale.

Since we started shooting, documentaries have been released about Bikram and Osho on Netflix, there an entire series on Vice about Yogi Bhajan and other yoga leaders who have exploited others, and last month, there was a Rolling Stone article about another one, Bentinho.

I hope you enjoy our labor of love…and maybe get the chorus stuck in your head.

description:
At Gastech 2023, which takes place in Singapore on 5-8 September, the global  energy community will discuss how hydrogen can be a key contributor to a diverse  energy mix in the future.

To reap the benefits of decarbonisation, hydrogen will need to be adopted in mobility, transportation, and electricity production. Singapore, which has just launched an ambitious national hydrogen plan, is the ideal place to promote your company’s hydrogen ambitions, and secure its position as a leader within the hydrogen value chain.

title: The Other Side of Ego | Jonathan Gravenor | TEDxOcala
description:
As he stared at the end of his life when diagnosed with cancer, Jonathan was hit with the fact he was not the man he thought he was - He had become the kind of man he would not want to be near. Two remarkable people appeared and taught him life's greatest lessons, and in that started him on the road to redemption that saved his soul and saved and his life. that started him on the road to redemption that saved his soul and saved and his life.
This television journalist seemed to have everything, until that everything included cancer. Jonathan writes about his intimate journey with a deadly disease. And he also tells a bigger story about how the disease launched him on a pilgrimage to become a better man. He uses his gifts, as a raconteur to show how some of the answers about how to survive his cancer were revealed in his quest for redemption.
He published his first book in 2017 – The Other Side of Ego. This talk was given at a TEDx event using the TED conference format but independently organized by a local community. Learn more at https://www.ted.com/tedx

title: Climate Engineering Or Weather Warfare? Testimony From Top Experts
description:
https://www.GeoengineeringWatch.org
To support Geoengineering Watch: http://www.geoengineeringwatch.org/support/
Contact us: Dane Wigington, P.O. Box 9, Bella Vista, CA, 96008
Please LIKE, SUBSCRIBE and CLICK THE BELL to ensure you are notified of our new videos. https://www.youtube.com/@DaneWigington

To read or post comments on this video, please go directly to the article: https://www.geoengineeringwatch.org/most-famous-geoengineer-its-really-not-a-moral-hazard-its-more-like-free-riding-on-our-grandkids/
Our hope and goal is for this video to be forwarded far and wide. DO NOT re-upload any part of this copyrighted video.

Top geoengineering scientists claim climate engineering is just a dangerous proposal and not an ongoing devastating reality. Are we to believe what they tell us? St. Louis-based rapper Daemon presents "Vader", his new single produced by Grills. Daemon marries a golden-era hiphop pedigree with a trailblazing spirit, routinely weaving genres as disparate as EDM, trap and grunge into the mix. Daemon has collaborated with artists like Killer Mike, DJ Shadow and Trackstar The DJ of Run The Jewels, who contributes cuts to "Vader". 2020 presidential candidate Bernie Sanders used Daemon's song "Feel Good" for his walk-out music for a TV interview. Daemon's work has been featured on Netflix (“Inventing Anna,” “Daybreak,” and “Work It”), FOX (“Ghosted”), Starz (“Power”), ads for Mini Cooper and Sephora, and TBS (on the Jordan Peele produced “The Last O.G.”). His track “Turn the World Around" was featured in Xbox exclusive Forza Horizon 5. "'Vader' started as a freestyle until the producer, Grills, thought it could be more," Daemon says. "I wanted to speak with love and care about the struggles I have with my city and the struggles folks in my city have to go through simultaneously. The dark and the light are all connected." "Vader" is out now on BLK BREAKFAST.
